description:
After coming to an understanding of the book of Daniel, William Miller resisted the call to preach for many years. As he continued to study, he concluded that Jesus would come around the years 1843 and 1844. After a series of events compelled him to 'tell the world' about Jesus' soon return. 

To find out more about William Miller please read our extended article on your website. https://lineagejourney.com/read/william-miller-study-and-call-to-ministry/
